name: Gurudatta   Engineering
overview: Gurudatta Engineering is from last 15 years in Manufacturing and Supplying Slotted Angles & Accessories for Storage Racks, Heavy Duty Racks, Mobile racks, Cable Trays, Cupboard, Industrial lockers etc. We used Raw material i.e. Steel, Chemical, Paints, Packing Material from reputed companies. We purchased C.R. Coils, H.R. Coils from reputed manufacturer like SAIL / ESSAR STEEL / ISPAT etc. We have complete manufacturing unit which includes Power Press, Shearing Machine and Bending Machine etc, with separated Painting Booth. We used 3 in one chemical to remove Oil, Gears & Dust on Sheet. Then we coat Red Oxide on product before painting. These system has exclusive design which has been evolved to optimize maximum storage of your product within minimum space, with minimum cost.
